show.description: One late-night rescue sparks a storm of emotions between a fearless student and her brother’s enigmatic best friend. As college games turn cruel and her secrets go public, the fallout is brutal—until he stands by her. "When Vivaan Stepped In" is a tale of heartbreak, hidden desire, and the fierce power of unexpected loyalty.
